name: Shaker_Series_24-inch_Natural_Finish_2.5-inch_Deep_Inside_On_The_Wall_Cabinet
reviews: It's great that this can hold so many boxes of Band-Aids and tubes of sunscreen and bottles of Wen oils! We have a very small bathroom and this cabinet has such a low profile that we found a spot for it. We painted it white, and to keep it as shallow as possible, did not nail on the nice wood back provided. I just ordered a longer one to store my husbands ties (leaving the shelves out). We have purchased the recessed cabinets, too, and they are wonderful but don 't work in every situation. This shallow cabinet is just great!
description:
Ideal as a medicine cabinet, spice cabinet, or storage cabinet anywhere the Shaker Series On The Wall cabinet is the perfect choice. This functional 24-inch cabinet mounts onto a wall with built-in cleats inside, for an easy installation.
Two (2) fully adjustable glass shelvesShaker style door sits on concealed hingesDoor has not been drilled for a knob or handle so you can mount it to open either directionPerfect as a medicine cabinet, spice cabinet, or storage cabinet anywhereBuilt-in cleats for an easy installationSolid maple doorMaterials: Wood/glassFinish: Natural pine, can be painted or stainedInside cabinet depth: 2.5 inchesDimensions: 25.5 inches high x 15.25 inches wide x 3.25 inches deepMaterialWoodTypeWall CabinetFinishNatural Finish
